    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved potatoes</strong> to a pot with plenty of<strong> boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 12-15 min or until fork-tender, then drain, return to the pot and set aside for later</p>",
