    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> finely</p><p>Wash the<strong> lettuce </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper, then remove your <strong>outer lettuce leaves </strong>and tear into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Finely shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p>",
