    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cultured coconut</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>mango chutney</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander stalks</strong>, <strong>sultanas</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>coronation mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
