    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice of the <strong>remaining lime </strong>with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>lime dressing</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>chickpeas</strong></p>",
