    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>lettuce</strong> <strong>leaves</strong>, <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong> and <strong>sliced cucumber</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> lime dressing</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>crunchy salad</strong></p>",
